<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Smell1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Smell,</orth> subst. 1) the sense of which the nose is the organ: <bibl n="shak. ven 441" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 441</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 141.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 141, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 132</bibl>.<lb />2) odor, the manner of affecting the olfactory organ: <bibl n="shak. ven 165" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 165" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 165</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 69.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 69, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.98.5" default="NO" valid="yes">98, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 4, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.297" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 297</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.94" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 114</bibl> (<emph>if I keep not my rank, -- Thou losest thy old s.;</emph> see Rank subst. 3). <bibl n="shak. jn 4.3.113" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 3, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.3.103" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 3, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.3.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 3, 46</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 56</bibl></cit>. == scent: <bibl n="shak. ven 686" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 686</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 686" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 686</bibl> <bibl n="shak. luc 695" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 695</bibl>.
